message: >
  If you reference or build upon this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
  Note that this is a proposed proof framework under active review; please cite accordingly.
title: "Riemann Hypothesis via Spectral Coherence"
abstract: >
  A proposed spectral-coherence framework for the Riemann Hypothesis, organized for
  mathematical audit, formalization, and review. The manuscript develops a proposed
  proof linking the functional symmetry of the Riemann zeta function to a
  spectral-coherence interpretation of the critical line Re(s) = 1/2.
